<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch ewr knecht <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Vorster fürbracht hab, daz er in
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuss</expan> gen uns süll sein,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> er geleyts zu uns begert sich
                            <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>antwten</expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und wenn <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">C.</expan>
<expan>Vorst<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">sand Marie Magdalene tag schierist</q>22.07.1420</note>
</app> zu uns <add><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan></add> meynt <expan>zu
                                kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so sol er umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu und von uns für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on geverde drey tag geleyt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        sein red <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
